name: black face needlepoint pillow
description:
French handmade pillow 23 cm x 26 cm
neon wool cross stitch, needlepoint
blue linen backside
original picture, only one !
In my work i combine the traditional old technique of needlepoint with a freshness of modern design.
Realization of my each project involves laborious, patient and precise covering by hand of canvas with stitches and takes many hours to complete just a few square inches.
As every of my works is handmade, it makes it absolutly unique and one of the kind
